verbose_text: Furthermore, our data showed that AAV9 mediated inhibition of miR-433 could significantly preserve left ventricular EF and FS, and reduce increased systolic LVID and diastolic LVID in mice 3 weeks post-MI (Supplemental Table XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY).
evidence: AAV9-mediated inhibition of miR-433 could significantly preserve left ventricular EF and FS
